{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":37295,"text":"(Hammer)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43184,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64076,"text":"(Microwave beeps) (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75696,"text":"You probably all agree with me"},{"time":77721,"text":"that this is a very nice road."},{"time":80496,"text":"It's made of asphalt,"},{"time":82655,"text":"and asphalt is a very nice material to drive on,"},{"time":85889,"text":"but not always, especially not on these days as today,"},{"time":90023,"text":"when it's raining a lot."},{"time":91874,"text":"Then you can have a lot of splash water in the asphalt."},{"time":94822,"text":"And especially if you then ride with your bicycle,"},{"time":97116,"text":"and pass these cars, then that's not very nice."},{"time":101061,"text":"Also, asphalt can create a lot of noise."},{"time":104171,"text":"It's a noisy material,"},{"time":105785,"text":"and if we produce roads like in the Netherlands,"},{"time":108229,"text":"very close to cities, then we would like a silent road."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112361,"text":"The solution for that is to make roads"},{"time":115630,"text":"out of porous asphalt."},{"time":117807,"text":"Porous asphalt, a material that we use now"},{"time":119798,"text":"in most of the highways in the Netherlands,"},{"time":122757,"text":"it has pores and water can just rain through it,"},{"time":126201,"text":"so all the rainwater will flow away to the sides,"},{"time":129102,"text":"and you have a road that's easy to drive on,"},{"time":131191,"text":"so no splash water anymore."},{"time":133121,"text":"Also the noise will disappear in these pores."},{"time":136283,"text":"Because it's very hollow, all the noise will disappear,"},{"time":139306,"text":"so it's a very silent road."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141894,"text":"It also has disadvantages, of course,"},{"time":145439,"text":"and the disadvantage of this road is that raveling can occur."},{"time":149601,"text":"What is raveling? You see that in this road"},{"time":152526,"text":"that the stones at the surface come off."},{"time":155147,"text":"First you get one stone, then several more,"},{"time":160425,"text":"and more and more and more and more,"},{"time":162167,"text":"and then they -- well, I will not do that. (Laughter)"},{"time":165734,"text":"But they can damage your windshield,"},{"time":168648,"text":"so you're not happy with that."},{"time":170438,"text":"And finally, this raveling can also lead to more and more damage."},{"time":174428,"text":"Sometimes you can create potholes with that."},{"time":177044,"text":"Ha. He's ready."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181105,"text":"Potholes, of course, that can become a problem,"},{"time":184290,"text":"but we have a solution."},{"time":185833,"text":"Here you see actually how the damage appears in this material."},{"time":189091,"text":"It's a porous asphalt, like I said, so you have only"},{"time":191091,"text":"a small amount of binder between the stones."},{"time":193863,"text":"Due to weathering, due to U.V. light, due to oxidation,"},{"time":197182,"text":"this binder, this bitumen,"},{"time":199910,"text":"the glue between the aggregates is going to shrink,"},{"time":202583,"text":"and if it shrinks, it gets micro-cracks,"},{"time":204528,"text":"and it delaminates from the aggregates."},{"time":206250,"text":"Then if you drive over the road, you take out the aggregates --"},{"time":208810,"text":"what we just saw here."},{"time":211806,"text":"To solve this problem, we thought of self-healing materials."},{"time":215620,"text":"If we can make this material self-healing,"},{"time":218281,"text":"then probably we have a solution."},{"time":221474,"text":"So what we can do is use steel wool just to clean pans,"},{"time":226068,"text":"and the steel wool we can cut in very small pieces,"},{"time":229553,"text":"and these very small pieces we can mix to the bitumen."},{"time":233457,"text":"So then you have asphalt"},{"time":235202,"text":"with very small pieces of steel wool in it."},{"time":238269,"text":"Then you need a machine, like you see here,"},{"time":241060,"text":"that you can use for cooking -- an induction machine."},{"time":244199,"text":"Induction can heat, especially steel; it's very good at that."},{"time":248248,"text":"Then what you do is you heat up the steel,"},{"time":250930,"text":"you melt the bitumen,"},{"time":252421,"text":"and the bitumen will flow into these micro-cracks,"},{"time":254987,"text":"and the stones are again fixed to the surface."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258194,"text":"Today I use a microwave because I cannot take"},{"time":262156,"text":"the big induction machine here onstage."},{"time":264393,"text":"So a microwave is a similar system."},{"time":267273,"text":"So I put the specimen in, which I'm now going to take out"},{"time":270918,"text":"to see what happened."},{"time":274170,"text":"So this is the specimen coming out now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276663,"text":"So I said we have such an industrial machine in the lab"},{"time":281056,"text":"to heat up the specimens."},{"time":283328,"text":"We tested a lot of specimens there,"},{"time":285418,"text":"and then the government, they actually saw our results,"},{"time":288593,"text":"and they thought, \"Well, that's very interesting. We have to try that.\""},{"time":292543,"text":"So they donated to us a piece of highway,"},{"time":294859,"text":"400 meters of the A58, where we had to make"},{"time":298346,"text":"a test track to test this material."},{"time":300856,"text":"So that's what we did here. You see where we were making the test road,"},{"time":304388,"text":"and then of course this road will last several years"},{"time":308886,"text":"without any damage. That's what we know from practice."},{"time":312174,"text":"So we took a lot of samples from this road"},{"time":314953,"text":"and we tested them in the lab."},{"time":317222,"text":"So we did aging on the samples,"},{"time":320139,"text":"did a lot of loading on it, healed them with our induction machine,"},{"time":323751,"text":"and healed them and tested them again."},{"time":326577,"text":"Several times we can repeat that."},{"time":328481,"text":"So actually, the conclusion from this research is that"},{"time":330706,"text":"if we go on the road every four years"},{"time":334024,"text":"with our healing machine -- this is the big version"},{"time":336904,"text":"we have made to go on the real road --"},{"time":338809,"text":"if we go on the road every four years"},{"time":340679,"text":"we can double the surface life of this road,"},{"time":344429,"text":"which of course saves a lot of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346606,"text":"Well, to conclude, I can say"},{"time":348783,"text":"that we made a material"},{"time":351539,"text":"using steel fibers, the addition of steel fibers,"},{"time":355319,"text":"using induction energy to really"},{"time":357828,"text":"increase the surface life of the road,"},{"time":360495,"text":"double the surface life you can even do,"},{"time":362245,"text":"so it will really save a lot of money with very simple tricks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365909,"text":"And now you're of course curious if it also worked."},{"time":369382,"text":"So we still have the specimen here. It's quite warm."},{"time":372485,"text":"Actually, it still has to cool down first"},{"time":375064,"text":"before I can show you that the healing works."},{"time":377404,"text":"But I will do a trial."},{"time":380272,"text":"Let's see. Yeah, it worked."},{"time":383031,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":384381,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}